dc_description_s: This data represents buildings for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2019. [The building footprints dataset was developed in 2005 along with the aerial imagery that was flown the same year. The data was created by Ayres in the spring of 2010 with Calumet County adding to the attribute table some time after.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-calumet.hub.arcgis.com/
